n fare perfect for refueling after skiing, including homemade soups, grilled meats, and decadent Swiss chocolate desserts. The Terrace Bar offers après-ski drinks and light bites with outdoor seating and fire pits, while our Cigar Lounge provides a sophisticated setting for evening cognac and conversation. In summer, we offer alfresco dining on our garden terrace with views of wildflower meadows.\n\nThe hotel\'s wellness facilities are designed to help you relax and rejuvenate in the mountain air. Our Alpine Spa features a heated indoor pool with underwater music and windows overlooking the mountains, a Finnish sauna, a steam room infused with Swiss pine essence, and a relaxation room with heated loungers. The spa menu includes treatments using Swiss Alpine herbs and minerals, including the signature Alpine Stone Massage using heated stones from local mountains. We also offer sports massages perfect for tired ski legs, and beauty treatments using Swiss skincare brands. The fitness center includes cardio equipment, free weights, and a yoga studio offering daily classes. In winter, we provide a ski concierge service, equipment storage with boot warmers, and can arrange private ski instructors and guides.\n\nAlpine Retreat\'s location in Verbier provides access to some of Europe\'s best skiing and summer activities. In winter, ski directly from our door to lifts accessing the Four Valleys ski area, known for challenging runs and reliable snow conditions. Our ski concierge can arrange heli-skiing, off-piste guides, and ski touring adventures. After skiing, explore Verbier\'s vibrant après-ski scene or relax at the hotel. In summer, the mountains transform into a paradise for hiking, with trails ranging from gentle valley walks to challenging alpine routes. We can arrange mountain biking, paragliding, golf at nearby courses, and excursions to charming Swiss villages. The hotel offers a kids\' club with activities and supervision, making it perfect for families. With our shuttle service to Verbier village, heated underground parking, and a team of multilingual staff dedicated to creating memorable mountain experiences, Alpine Retreat is your ultimate Swiss Alps sanctuary.',
